data.description: Excellent opportunity to own a beautiful horse farm on 18.899 acres! Property line runs along creek!! Beautiful 5 bed,2 full bath home with granite counter tops,large back deck, new metal roof and  whole house automatic back up propane generator! Two fenced in horse barns with water and electric, tack room & outdoor arena. 2 sheds & 2 run ins. Barns are 40 x 30  & 36 X 36 and a 40 X 12 lean to! Property also includes an electrical box for camper hook up! Located 5 minutes from Wilmington Air Par
